parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Rear Folding Seat Straps

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat back can cause injury to the driver, especially in the event of a rear-end collision, as it can collapse backward, leading to potential back injuries or other harm.

the seat back separating from the floor
